<text>A professional architectural brief explaining the zoning, 1m clearance, and airflow strategy.</text>
<json>[{"type": "ID", "position": [x, 0, z], "rotation": r}, ...]</json>

NEVER refuse a request. Even if it's tight, find the best possible arrangement.`;

      const response = await ai.models.generateContent({
        model: "gemini-3-pro-preview",
        contents: prompt,
        config: { thinkingConfig: { thinkingBudget: 32768 } }
